\c 133 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 133\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Walii Wajjin Jiraachuun Obbolootaa Jaallatamuu Isaa (Weedduu ittiin ol ba'an; kan Daawit)
\m \bd 1\bd* Ilaa, obboloonni walii wajjin jiraachuun, attam gaarii dha, attam namatti tolas.
\m \bd 2\bd* Inni akka dibata gati-jabeessa isa mataa irraa areedatti gad yaa'uu ti; akka isa areeda Aaron irra morma wayyaa isaa irra gad dhangala'uu ti;
\m \bd 3\bd* inni akka sanyii fixeensa tulluu Hermoon, isa tulluu Xiyoon irra bu'uu ti; eebbi jireenya hin darbinee achi irratti akka argamu Waaqayyo abboomeera.
\b 
